============ Setup the RUST env in Windows ============
1. Install the rustup
https://static.rust-lang.org/rustup/dist/x86_64-pc-windows-msvc/rustup-init.exe

2. Install the Microsoft C++ build tools
https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/visual-cpp-build-tools/
  a - 勾選「使用 C++ 的桌面開發」
  b - 語言套件改勾選「英文」

3. Set rustup & cargo to windows env
Ex:
  a - C:\Users\mickey\.rustup\toolchains\stable-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc\bin
  b - C:\Users\mickey\.cargo\bin
  c - Check your installation
    |- rustc --version
  d - keep your Rust installation up to date
    |- rustup update

4. Recommand the Visual studio code for further develop
5. Install the plug-in "rust-analyzer" in VS code

6. Using the cargo new to create a new project
cargo new hello_world
cd hello_world

7. Using Cargo build to build Rust project.
cargo build

8. Using Cargo run to launch Rust project.
cargo run

Ref:
https://hackmd.io/@yipo/HyWGoEfsu
